                    <p>China Eastern Airlines officially known as China Eastern Airlines Corporation Limited is the second-largest carrier in China. The airline is headquartered in the China Eastern Airlines Building, on the grounds of Shanghai Hongqiao International Airport in Changning District, Shanghai. It has a strong presence on routes in Asia, North America, and Australia & has also launched direct flights from Shanghai to Prague, Amsterdam, Madrid, and St. Petersburg. </p>
